	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-174408485" class="story-title"> <a   href="//yro.slashdot.org/story/24/07/07/186222/jeff-bezoss-move-from-wa-to-fl-has-saved-him-close-to-1b-in-taxes-this-year">Jeff Bezos's Move From WA To FL Has Saved Him Close To $1B in Taxes This Year</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.geekwire.com/2024/jeff-bezos-keeps-selling-amazon-stock-after-announcing-his-move-out-of-washington-state/"  title="External link - https://www.geekwire.com/2024/jeff-bezos-keeps-selling-amazon-stock-after-announcing-his-move-out-of-washington-state/" target="_blank"> (geekwire.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
		<!--<span class="comments commentcnt-174408485" >70</span>-->
		

		
		<!-- comment bubble -->
		
			<span class="comment-bubble"><a href="//yro.slashdot.org/story/24/07/07/186222/jeff-bezoss-move-from-wa-to-fl-has-saved-him-close-to-1b-in-taxes-this-year#comments" title="">70</a></span>
		
	</h2>
	<div class="details" id="details-174408485">
		<span class="story-details">
		<span class="story-views">
			<span class="sodify" onclick="firehose_set_options('color', 'red')" title="Filter Firehose to entries rated red or better"></span><span class="icon-beaker pop1 " alt="Popularity" title="Filter Firehose to entries rated red or better" onclick="firehose_set_options('color', 'red')"><span></span></span> 
		</span>
		</span>
		<span class="story-byline">
	
				
			Posted
				by 
		
		
			
				  EditorDavid
			
		
		

		
		
		<time id="fhtime-174408485" datetime="on Sunday July 07, 2024 @02:42PM">on Sunday July 07, 2024 @02:42PM</time>
		
		
			 from the <span class="dept-text">billionaire's-budget</span> dept.
		
		</span>
	</div>
</header>

<div class="body" id="fhbody-174408485">
	
		
	

	
		
		<div id="text-174408485" class="p">
			
		 	
				As Amazon's stock <a href="https://finance.yahoo.com/news/bezos-sell-5-billion-amazon-132129518.html">hits a record high</a> (rising 32% just this year), long-time Slashdot reader <a href="/~theodp">theodp</a> writes:

<i>GeekWire reports that <a href="https://www.geekwire.com/2024/jeff-bezos-keeps-selling-amazon-stock-after-announcing-his-move-out-of-washington-state/">Jeff Bezos keeps selling Amazon stock after announcing his move away from Washington state</a> &mdash; and its 7% tax on capital gains of more than $262,000 from the sale of stocks and bonds &mdash; to Florida, which does not have a capital gains tax (like WA, FL also does not tax personal income).<br> <br>Taylor Soper writes, "Bezos saved more than $600 million by <a href="https://news.slashdot.org/story/24/02/09/2154258/with-miami-move-jeff-bezos-proves-zip-codes-do-matter">moving to Miami and avoiding Washington's capital gains tax</a>, CNBC reported in February, based on his sale of 50 million shares [$8.5 billion] earlier this year. With the sale of 25 million additional shares [$5 billion], revealed this week in a regulatory filing, Bezos will likely have saved close to $1 billion in total so far. It's a giant chunk of change that would have otherwise gone to the state of Washington."</i><br>
		 	
		</div>

		

		

		
			
		
	</div>
	<aside class="grid_24 view_mode">
		
